english.title: the moon of this country
text: the moon of this country! the eyes of its nights!
i am alone up late at night singing for her
wherever i go , my heart always
the moon of this country! the eyes of its nights!
i am alone up late at night singing for her

She is the country where i live in
so in love with her calling her
and she is in my heart forever
